<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[Why does Dolores feel relief, when she finds out that Nichole lied about crash? <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
